data.description: BONUS BONUS!! With AB 1033 being singed this property is a perfect fit for splitting the ADU and selling both units or keeping one and selling the other  Great investment opportunity     This inviting home boasts an open-concept living room and kitchen, perfect for modern living and effortless entertaining. The seamless flow between these spaces creates a warm and inviting atmosphere, allowing for gatherings with friends and family.  Front house features large open kitchen with dining nook and living room access as well as 3 spacious bedrooms and a large upgraded bathroom.     Step outside, and you'll find easy access to a spacious backyard, ideal for family entertainment and outdoor activities complete with patio area and above ground pool.  Whether it's a barbecue, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air, this backyard offers ample room to relax and play, this is a space to call your own.     Off the 2 car garage is a 1 bed 1 bath home perfect for in laws or to rent out and cover a good portion of your mortgage. This ADU has been recently upgraded with new bathroom, carpet and paint and is in move in ready condition!!    One of the standout features of this home is the stunning Mountain View, visible from both the front and backyard. You can wake up to the majestic sight of mountains on a daily basis, creating a serene and picturesque backdrop and spending the day enjoying or entertaining in the great yard.    Additionally, the property offers a spacious driveway and a designated RV/Trailer parking area, providing ample parking space for multiple vehicles and outdoor enthusiasts. This home is a blend of comfort, convenience, and natural beauty, making it a perfect choice for those seeking a well-rounded lifestyle.
